OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FIt will be a
OL,6,Fbright end to the day then a dry and
OL,7,Fchilly night with long clear spells.
OL,8,FCloud will increase later across
OL,9,FShetland.
OL,10,
OL,11,CFriday:FMostly cloudy and rather cold
OL,12,Fover Shetland with a few showers
OL,13,Farriving from the north. Mainly dry
OL,14,Fand bright over Orkney.
OL,15,
OL,16,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FMainly
OL,17,Fdry but rather cold and cloudy over
OL,18,Fthe weekend with the odd shower.
OL,19,FMilder on Monday with some patchy rain.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
